	 "ROB_BELMONT_WINGEDBOOTS_NAME": "Pegasus Boots",
	 "ROB_BELMONT_WINGEDBOOTS_DESC": "After <style=cIsUtility>1</style> second of sprinting while <style=cIsUtility>grounded</style>, gain <style=cIsDamage>12 movement speed</style>. Hitting an enemy with <style=cIsDamage>Rush</style> causes you to kick them <style=cIsUtility>into the air</style> and then away, for <style=cIsDamage>4x200%</style> and <style=cIsDamage>300%</style> damage.",
	 "ROB_BELMONT_WINGEDBOOTS_PICKUP": "Boots that upgrade your secondary skill and enable you to run like the wind.",
